  "texts": [
    "On the other hand, ADL-LLM leverages the common-sense knowledge implicitly encoded in the LLM, and it is capable of recognizing these activities without any type of training.Figures 6 and 7 depict the confusion matrices of zero-shot ADL-LLM, that can be used to inspect the results more closely.",
    "Considering the UCI-ADL dataset, the most challenging activity in both homes is snacking.",
    "This phenomenon is evident in the confusion matrices depicted in Figure 6.",
    "Indeed, snacking is often confused with other food-related activities like preparing breakfast since they share similar sensor patterns.",
    "In the Home B of the UCI ADL dataset, the relaxing on couch activity is associated with a high number of false positives."
